1. *Milijuna* ljudi je izašlo na ulice da bi protestovalo (A million people took to the streets to protest).
2. On je zaradio *milijun* dolara (He earned a million dollars).
3. U zemlji ima *milijuni* malih firmi (There are millions of small businesses in the country).
4. *Milijunima* ljudi je omogućeno da dobiju besplatne lekove (Millions of people were provided with free medicines).
5. Ona je nedostajala svojoj porodici *milijun* puta (She missed her family a million times).